text: This plate for only $2.80. Definitely value for money. Most items sell for only 60c each. Stall manned by 2 old aunties and 1 old uncle. Definitely will be back to support! Please support too!

A simple and traditional fried mee hoon / thick noodles store located on level 2 of this hawker centre. Choices of food to go along can be plain veg, sunny side up egg, luncheon meat, fried chicken wing, etc. All in very affordable price. Served by old ladies and always draw a crowd of young and old.

20 - 30 years store. Very unique taste nasi lemak.
Definitely will miss it when they retire.
